  <section class="responsibility">
    <h2>Responsibility</h2>
    <p>
      The money, opportunity and innovation left on the table when human potential goes untapped matters not just
      commercially, but humanly. When people invite me into their organisations, teams or leadership challenges, they’re
      trusting me with something important. I don’t take that lightly. If this way of working resonates, then we’re
